desc: In the seaside village of Ogunquit, Maine, The Lazy Daisy is a women's boutique that is filled with unique clothing and accessories for all ages. You will find classic to contemporary clothing by designers such as Samuel Dong, Tulip, Wooden Ships, xcvi, Nally & Millie, Z Supply, Lola Jewelry, Scout bags and more!

layout.text: Intricately designed jewelry comprised of Austrian Swarovski crystals with Japanese and Czech glass beads.
